           <h3>General Terms for Drivers</h3>
These General Terms set forth the main terms and conditions applying to and governing the agreement between you (hereinafter referred to as "you" or "Driver") and Izzicab regarding usage of the Izzicab Driver's App for the purpose of providing Transportation Services.

In order to provide Transportation Services via using the Izzicab App you must agree to the terms and conditions that are set forth below.

<h3>1. DEFINITIONS</h3>
1.1. Izzicab (also referred to as "we", "our" or "us") – a private limited company incorporated and registered under the laws of Federal repulic of Nigeria with registration code xxxxxxxx, registered office Office address 48/50 ogbuefi nwakoby street nkwelle ezunaka Oyi local government, Anambra State.
<br>
1.2. Affiliate – means an entity that is directly or indirectly under the control of Izzicab and who provides certain Izzicab Services in a city. Overview regarding which Affiliate provides Izzicab Services in which specific state or city and their contact details can be accessed at http://Izzicab.com/cities.
<br>
1.3. Izzicab Services – services that Izzicab and/or its Affiliates provide you, including provision and maintenance of the Izzicab App and the Izzicab platform, client support, mediation of the payments and communication between you and the Customer or other similar support services as described in these General Terms or the Agreement.
<br>
1.4. Izzicab App –In the meaning of these General Terms, Izzicab App refers to the Izzicab Drivers App, which the Drivers use to receive and accept requests and manage Transportation Services.
<br>
1.5. Customer – a person requesting Transportation Services by using the Izzicab mobile application.
<br>
1.6. Driver or you – the person providing Transportation Services via the Izzicab App. Please note that you may register the account either as a legal or a natural person.
<br>
1.7. General Terms – the terms and conditions provided in this document.
<br>
1.8. Agreement – any agreement between you and Izzicab regarding the use of the Izzicab App. The Agreement consists of these General Terms, Privacy Policy, Drivers Guide and other additional terms and conditions or documents referred to herein or agreed in the future between you and Izzicab.
<br>
1.9. License – your right to use the Izzicab App and the Website in accordance with the Agreement.
<br>
1.10. Website – Izzicab's website located at www.Izzicab.com and www.izzicabapp.com and any of its subpages, including the Izzicab Driver's Portal.
<br>
1.11. Fare – the fee a Customer is obliged to pay you for provision of the Transportation Services.
<br>
1.12. Izzicab Fee – the fee you are obliged to pay to Izzicab for the right to use the Izzicab App. Izzicab Fee consists of a fee per each Customer order you have completed.
<br>
1.13. In-app Payment – a payment made by the Customer via the Izzicab App for the Transportation Services. The In-app Payment may be made by using bank/credit card, business, mobile carrier payment or any other electronic payment method enabled by Izzicab.
<br>
1.14. Izzicab Driver's Portal – a portal containing relevant information and documents regarding your usage of the Izzicab App in course of provision of Transportation Services, including accounting documentation. You may access Izzicab Driver's Portal at http://partners.Izzicab.com by entering your user name and password.
<br>
1.15. Transportation Services – the transportation service you are providing to the Customer whose request you have accepted via the Izzicab App.


